== Treatment of abdominal aortic aneurysms==

Indications for elective surgical reconstruction:
The outer diameter of the aneurysm> = 4 cm
Outer diameter of aneurysm <4 cm and an increase of 0.5 cm in 6 months
Perioperative mortality rate of 3-5%
Alternative to surgical treatment - arthroplasty (CFR 1.5-2%)

Conservative therapy is indicated for:
Aneurysm diameter <4 cm
Increasing the diameter of less than 2 mm 


